          "component_id": "gallery_character",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/25750596/f9787bcb392a2d1ac54d64f66aefcc1e_2005473294052391126.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>A kind of impenetrable shield known in Inazuma as a Thunder Barrier.<br>For some mysterious reason, receiving the acknowledgment of <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Electrograna</span> and carrying them with you allows you to pass through some such barriers unimpeded.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/25750596/5af020a7357aab1f50aae85c64708eab_7060941506539507912.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>However, some strong barriers can only be traversed with much stronger Electrograna. Perhaps offering <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Electro Sigils</span> to the Sacred Sakura at the Grand Narukami Shrine will one day allow you to pass through all areas shut off by Thunder Barriers.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/25750596/d743efd4c667be22669504744a02cc63_5517454035374251551.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Some Thunder Barriers seal Thunderstones within them.<br>These fragments of raw, unbridled energy can be temporarily suppressed with Electrograna. <br>While a Thunderstone is suppressed, the Thunder Barrier around it is removed.</p>",
                "key": "Page 3/3"
              }
            ],
            "pic": ""
          }
        }
